@startuml SD-11_Remediation_Plan

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

actor       "User"            as User
participant "Web\nUI"         as UI
participant "Insights\nBackend" as Back
participant "Gemini\nAPI"     as Gemini
database    "DB"              as DB

== Remediation Guide Generation ==

User -> UI   : Click "Get Remediation Guide"\non a finding
UI   -> Back : GET /api/ai/remediation/:findingId

Back -> DB   : find Finding + Scan + Asset\n(verify org ownership)
DB  --> Back : context data

Back -> Back : Build prompt:\n"Generate detailed remediation for:\nVuln: [name], Severity: [sev],\nTarget: [asset.value]"

Back -> Gemini : generateContent(prompt)\n[temp: 0.2, maxTokens: 4096]
Gemini --> Back : JSON remediation guide

Back -> Back : parseJson(response)\n→ { title, steps[],\nverification, references[] }

Back --> UI  : 200 OK (remediation guide)
UI  --> User : Display step-by-step guide\nwith code examples

@enduml
